				"description": "Validate a SWIFT message against SR2024 standards.\n\n**Checks:**\n- Field presence (mandatory/optional)\n- Field formats and lengths\n- Character sets\n- Business rules\n\n**Returns:**\n- Validation status\n- List of errors\n- List of warnings"
			},
